# How to Clone?

For clone you need to write this command on your Git terminal on the folder that you want to copy:

```
git clone https://github.com/InternetX-browser/ix_assets.git
```

## I can clone?

Yes, you can clone this repository.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> If you clone a repository, you have a copy with all assets and you can edit all folders or assets.
